## 7. Summary Table — Every Scenario at a Glance

| Scenario | Stripe action | New `payments` row? | New `payout_batch_items` row? | Xero action |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Client charged (new inspection) | Payment Intent | Yes (`Charge`) | — | Create invoice |
| Scout paid (full) | Connect Transfer | — | Yes (`Payout`) | Create bill |
| Client refunded (full) | Refund | Yes (`Refund`, linked) | — | Credit note |
| Client refunded (partial) | Refund (partial amount) | Yes (`PartialRefund`, linked) | — | Credit note (partial) |
| Dispute = Mistake, pre-payout | Refund (Client) | Yes (`Refund`/`PartialRefund`) | Yes (`Payout`, full amount, proceeds normally) | Credit note + bill |
| Dispute = Fraud, pre-payout | Refund (Client) | Yes (`Refund`/`PartialRefund`) | **None created** — Scout never paid | Credit note only |
| Dispute = Fraud, post-payout (Case B) | Refund (Client) | Yes (`Refund`/`PartialRefund`) | Yes (`PayoutAdjustment`, record-keeping only — Spekto absorbs the loss, no actual clawback attempted) | Credit note (Client) + write-off/bad-debt entry (loss) |
| Marketplace purchase | Payment Intent | — (separate `marketplace_purchases` row, not `payments`) | — | Create invoice (separate revenue category) |

